* Table permissions
For default the pREST will serve in publish mode, making all tables and views visible.
But using prest.toml you can configure read/write/delete permissions of each table.

    [[access.tables]]
    name = "person"
    permissions = ["read", "write", "delete"]
    fields = ["id", "name"]

